custom_css_array.product_setting_section_shop_page_produc: .aux-shop-archive .products-loop .price .amount, .aux-shop-archive .products-loop .price ins .amount{ color:rgb(51, 204, 102); font-size:16px; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.24px; }

.aux-shop-archive .products-loop .price del,  .aux-shop-archive .products-loop .price del .amount{ color:rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size:16px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.24px; }
custom_css_array.product_setting_section_shop_page_result:
.woocommerce-page .woocommerce-result-count{ font-family:'Poppins'; color:rgb(32, 36, 46); font-size:30px; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.6px; } 
@media(max-width: 1024px){ .woocommerce-page .woocommerce-result-count{ font-size:20px; }  }
custom_css_array.product_setting_section_shop_page_sales_: .aux-shop-archive .products-loop .onsale{ font-family:'Red Hat Display'; color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:12px; font-weight:400; text-transform:capitalize; letter-spacing:-0.48px; line-height:4em; }
custom_css_array.sidebar_common_widget_title_typography: .aux-sidebar .widget-title{ color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:20px; font-weight:bold; text-transform:capitalize; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.9px; }
custom_css_array.product_setting_section_single_appearanc:
.single-product .price .amount, .single-product .price ins .amount{ color:rgb(51, 204, 102); font-size:36px; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.54px; } 
@media(max-width: 1024px){ .single-product .price .amount, .single-product .price ins .amount{ font-size:25px; }  }

.single-product .price del .amount, .single-product .price del{ color:rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size:16px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.24px; } 
@media(max-width: 1024px){ .single-product .price del .amount, .single-product .price del{ font-size:13px; }  }

.single-product .woocommerce-product-details__short-description{ color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size:16px; font-weight:500; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.48px; } 
@media(max-width: 1024px){ .single-product .woocommerce-product-details__short-description{ font-size:16px; }  }

.single-product .cart .auxshp-add-to-cart{ color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:15px; font-weight:500; text-transform:capitalize; line-height:1.4em; letter-spacing:-0.3px; } 
@media(max-width: 1024px){ .single-product .cart .auxshp-add-to-cart{ font-size:13px; }  }
custom_css_array.comment_forms_button_typo: #commentform .form-submit input[type="submit"]{ color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size:16px; font-weight:500; text-transform:capitalize; line-height:1.4em; }

custom_css_array.product_related_posts_label_typo:
.single-product .auxshp-related-products .widget-title{ font-family:'Red Hat Display'; color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size:50px; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.4em; } 
@media(max-width: 768px){ .single-product .auxshp-related-products .widget-title{ font-size:30px; }  }
custom_css_array.product_related_posts_price_typo: .aux-widget-related-products .auxshp-entry-main .price .amount , .aux-widget-related-products .auxshp-entry-main .price ins .amount{ color:rgb(51, 204, 102); font-size:16px; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.5em; letter-spacing:-0.24px; }
custom_css_array.product_related_posts_reg_price_typo: .aux-widget-related-products .auxshp-entry-main .price ins del,  .aux-widget-related-products .auxshp-entry-main .price del .amount{ color:rgba(153, 153, 153, 0.72); font-size:16px; font-weight:400; line-height:2em; letter-spacing:-0.24px; }

custom_css_array.single_post_content_typography:
.single-post .hentry .entry-content{ font-family:'Montserrat'; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size:16px; font-weight:500; line-height:1.6em; }

@media(max-width: 1024px){ .single-post .hentry footer.entry-meta .entry-tax a, .single-post .hentry footer.entry-meta .entry-tax i{ font-size:14px; }  }
custom_css_array.single_post_meta_typography:
.single-post .hentry footer.entry-meta .entry-tax{ font-size:20px; color:rgb(17, 31, 61); font-weight:400; text-transform:capitalize; font-style:normal; letter-spacing:-0.6px; }

A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy.
